        "Answer": "$$\\left .\\begin{matrix}{a}\\csc{\\theta} \\cos{} \\theta \\tan{} \\theta = ( \\frac{1}{\\sin{\\theta}} ) \\cos{} \\theta ( \\frac{\\sin{\\theta}}{\\cos{\\theta}} ) \\\\ \\text{quadquadquadquadquadquadquadquadquad\u00a0} = \\frac{\\cos{\\theta}}{\\sin{\\theta}} ( \\frac{\\sin{\\theta}}{\\cos{\\theta}} ) \\\\ \\text{quadquadquadquadquadquadquadquadquad\u00a0} = \\frac{\\sin{\\theta} \\cos{} \\theta}{\\sin{\\theta} \\cos{} \\theta} \\\\ \\text{quadquadquadquadquadquadquadquadquad\u00a0} = 1\\end{matrix}\\right .$$",
